des:
Hindi Jokes is a fun box of jokes. Listen to a number of jokes in Hindi audio when you open the skill on Alexa. These jokes will surely make you mood happy

To enable Hindi Jokes say “Alexa, enable Hindi Jokes”.

Play Hindi Jokes on Alexa in Hindi following the steps below:

1. Say 'Alexa, open Hindi Jokes'. Alexa will play a random joke.
